companies and worked on dozens of projects. I was involved in making

mBanking. I have done my part in telecommunication software working for 
Mera Software Services while upgrading old and making new iOS app for 
Avaya Inc. I was outsourced for some European and USA software companies 
with dozen of different projects where I would single out the projects 
for maintenance related use. Currently i am working in Progiton GmbH
